To build marlin:
    mkdir build
    cd build
    cmake ..
    make

To install it:
    su
    make install

    or, on sudo based distributions (Ubuntu for instance):
    sudo make install

Options:
    Debug build:
        cmake .. -DCMAKE_BUILD_TYPE=Debug

    Different prefix:
        cmake .. -DCMAKE_INSTALL_PREFIX=/opt
    
    Note that if you want to install libcore and libwidgets only
    you have to use the following command:
        cmake .. -DLIB_ONLY=true
